-- Dexia May Have French Units Nationalized, Financial Times Says
-- B y   C h r i s   S p i l l a n e
-- 2012-01-07T08:57:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-07/dexia-may-have-french-units-nationalized-financial-times-says.html
Dexia SA (DEXB) , the French-Belgian lender,
may have French parts of the bank nationalized, the Financial
Times reported, citing Michel Bouvard, chairman of Caisse des
Depôts et Consignations.  A nationalization plan was one option discussed for Dexia’s
French municipal finance unit, the newspaper reported Bouvard as
saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chris Spillane in  London  at 
 cspillane3@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
 Andrew Blackman  at 
 ablackman@bloomberg.net . 